name: Urushihara-lora001
description:
This is my first LoRA ever but Im pretty happy with the results ^^
It is trained to mimic Satoshi Urushihara style, but you may find it similar to many other anime styles... especially anime from the 90s ;)

I'd recommend using a weight value below 0.8.
For my tests I have used OrangeCocoaMix2_Hard.

Please feel free to try it out and let me know about it in the comments.
